OL,3,CTwo teenage boys among three to appear
OL,4,Cin court charged with murder
OL,6,FThey will all appear before Newcastle
OL,7,FCrown Court tomorrow.
OL,9,FFour others who were arrested have
OL,10,Fbeen released on bail.
